173→ * When `isWatched` is true (file watcher active via notify crate),
174→ * polling is disabled — cache invalidation comes from fs:changed events.
175→ * Falls back to 5s polling when not watched.
176→ *
177→ * IMPORTANT: Requires workspaceState === "ready" — same guard as useDiffStats.
178→ * See useDiffStats comment for the full explanation of the phantom diff race.
